flowchart LR
    A[Custom Element] --> B[static formAssociated = true]
    B --> C[attachInternals no constructor]
    C --> D[ElementInternals]
    D --> E[setFormValue define o valor]
    D --> F[setValidity define validacao]
    E --> G[FormData do formulario pai]
    F --> H[Constraint Validation do formulario pai]
